@startuml
' Diagram: F10 - Dashboard tong quan va monitoring CMS (Sequence)
' Status: WIP
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD b618c08
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), ResolveRange(), LoadPoiSectionAsync(), LoadAnalyticsWithRetryAsync(), LoadAnalyticsAsync(), LoadActivityAsync(), LoadGeoAsync(), LoadTopPoiAsync(), LoadRevenueAsync(), LoadSummaryAsync(), FillMissingBuckets()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/Index.cshtml
' Note: Sequence cap nhat dashboard hien tai: POI section + monitoring analytics dung raw Npgsql tren shared EF connection.
title F10 - Dashboard tong quan va monitoring CMS

actor Admin
participant "CMS IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant AppDbContext
participant "DbConnection/NpgsqlCommand" as Npgsql
database DB

Admin -> IndexModel: mo /?mode&date&week&month&year&from&to
IndexModel -> IndexModel: ResolveRange()

IndexModel -> AppDbContext: LoadPoiSectionAsync()\nPOIs.Include(MonAns)
AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT poi + monan ORDER BY MucUuTien
DB --> AppDbContext: POIs
IndexModel -> IndexModel: tinh TongPOI,\nTongMonAn,\nSoQuanQuaHan

IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadAnalyticsWithRetryAsync()
IndexModel -> AppDbContext: Database.GetDbConnection()
AppDbContext --> IndexModel: DbConnection
IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadActivityAsync(conn, since, until, granularity)
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT date_trunc, active_users,\nviews, visits FROM lichsuphat
DB --> Npgsql: ActivityBuckets

IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadGeoAsync(conn, since, until)
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT poi lat/lng/name,\nCOUNT(*) FROM lichsuphat JOIN poi
DB --> Npgsql: GeoPoints

IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadTopPoiAsync(conn, since, until)
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT top POI views/visits
DB --> Npgsql: TopPoi

IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadRevenueAsync(conn, since, until, granularity)
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT revenue tu dangkyapp va hoadon
DB --> Npgsql: RevenueBuckets

IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadSummaryAsync(conn, since, until)
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT active devices, views, visits
DB --> Npgsql: summary

IndexModel -> IndexModel: FillMissingBuckets()\nSerialize ActivityJson/GeoJson/RevenueJson
IndexModel --> Admin: render dashboard + monitoring section
@enduml
